$30 kyr, in which\ncase the asymmetry reverses with a period of $\\sim$125 kyr. Otherwise, the\norbital forcing does not produce a net asymmetry over longer timescales, and is\nnot a likely mechanism for generating the observed dichotomy.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 26 Dec 2014 22:08:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-12-30"}
